        </item>
        <item>
            <title>YouTube 一個動作背景播放教學，適用 iPhone Android 兩平台毋須 Premium</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/youtube-background-play-music/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=youtube-background-play-music</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/youtube-background-play-music/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 11:20:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Android App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[實用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[youtube]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285437</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>官方 YouTube 網站只需要一個動作，就可以幫你將音樂設定在背景播放，毋須 YouTube Premium 帳户或者其他破解。以下就介紹 iOS, Android 兩個平台的操作方法。</p><p>（由於軟件經常改變其運作方式，以下操作方式有可能在未來用不到，想穩陣的話最好當然是課金 YouTube Premium 了）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010671403-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010671403-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010671403.jpg 832w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><h2>iOS 平台操作方式</h2><p>iOS 用家首先用 Google Chome 瀏覽器打開 YouTube 網站，並於此打開影片。有動態島功能的 iPhone 可任意使用桌面版或流動版網站，如沒有動態島，請在 Chome 選項切換到桌面版網站。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p>返回主畫面，此時音樂會暫停播放。請在 2 秒內按住動態島，令它彈出，此時再按播放按鈕，便可使音樂再次播放。現在你可離開 YouTube 網站，或在關閉熒幕時，都可在背景繼續播放音樂。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-1-317x580.jpg" alt="" width="317" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-1-317x580.jpg 317w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-1-scaled.jpg 492w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 317px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲返回主畫面後馬上按住動態島</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-2-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-2-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-2-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在動態島通知按播放按鈕便可</p><p>在關閉畫面後，可在鎖機畫面的播放控制項中再次播放影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-3-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-3-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-3-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p>（沒有動態島功能的 iPhone，請在切換桌面版網站後，關閉熒幕，並於熒幕的控制項中重新播放音樂便可）</p><h2>操作教學影片：</h2><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="ios" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1044277838?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/youtube-background-play-music/tips-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
