            <title>【CES 2025】LG StanbyME 2 帶出街用的大電視    27 吋 1440P + 可用 4 小時</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/lg-stanbyme-2/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-stanbyme-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/lg-stanbyme-2/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 09:34:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LG StanbyME 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[便攜電視]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285398</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>LG 在 CES 2025 展示出推出第二代便攜式電視 LG StanbyME 2，設計讓用户能輕鬆攜帶或直接安裝於牆面。此款產品延續了趣味性和實用性的結合，吸引了不少科技愛好者的關注。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285401 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652935-347x580.jpg" alt="" width="347" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652935-347x580.jpg 347w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652935.jpg 539w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 347px" /></p><p>新款 StanbyME 2 採用 27 吋 16:9 螢幕，並提升至 1440p 解像度，相較上一代的 1080p，畫質表現進一步改良。同時電池續航時間從前代的 3.5 小時延長至 4 小時，為用户提供更多靈活使用空間。電視甚至可配合孭帶，可便攜帶出户外使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285402 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652947-383x580.jpg" alt="" width="383" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652947-383x580.jpg 383w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652947.jpg 595w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 383px" /></p><p>在配件方面，LG 引入一款類似於大型 iPad 的折疊式保護套，增加產品便攜性及多用途應用場景。此外，StanbyME 2 新增兩個 USB-C 接口，讓用户可以連接視像鏡頭等配件，進一步提升裝置的多功能性。遙控方面，則採用了磁吸設計，令使用體驗更為便捷。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_85096"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P45K999opDA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P45K999opDA">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
